section Section1;
shared _folder_DA = let
  Source = _folderPBIexVV,
  Navigation = Source{[Name = "DA"]}[Content],
  #"Sorted rows" = Table.Sort(Navigation, {{"Date created", Order.Descending}})
in
  #"Sorted rows";
shared fn_DA = let
  fn_DA = (source as binary) =>
let
    importExcel = Excel.Workbook(source){[Item="Export",Kind="Sheet"]}[Data],
    addCustom = Table.AddColumn(importExcel, "Custom", each try if Text.StartsWith([Column1], "Rakendatud filtrid:") then 1 else if Text.StartsWith([Column1], "Applied filters:") then 1 else 0 otherwise 0,  Int64.Type),
    position = List.PositionOf( addCustom[Custom], 1),
    getDate = let _text =  addCustom[Column1]{position},  dotPosition = Text.PositionOf(_text, "."), extract = Text.Range(_text , dotPosition-2, 10), dd = Text.Start(extract, 2), mm = Text.Middle(extract, 3, 2), yyyy=Text.End(extract, 4), result = Date.From(mm&"/"&dd&"/"&yyyy) in result,
    cleanTable = Table.PromoteHeaders (Table.RemoveColumns( Table.Range( addCustom,0,position-2), {"Column5", "Column6", "Column7", "Column8", "Column9", "Column10", "Custom"})),
    extractKava = Table.RenameColumns( Table.TransformColumns(cleanTable, {{"Õppekava + tähis", each Text.End(_, 4), type text}}), {"Õppekava + tähis", "kava"}),
    addKP =  Table.AddColumn(extractKava, "kp", each Date.AddDays( getDate,-1)),
    tranformColTypes = Table.TransformColumnTypes(addKP,{{"kava", type text}, {"Kvalifitseeruv kokku", Int64.Type}, {"Vastuvõetav", Int64.Type}, {"Kinnitanud õppima tuleku", Int64.Type}, {"kp", type date}})
in
    tranformColTypes
in
  fn_DA;

    #"Imported Excel Workbook" = Excel.Workbook(Custom1),

    cleanTable = Table.RemoveColumns( Table.Range( addCustom,0,position-2), {"Column5",  "Column6", "Column7", "Column8", "Column9", "Column10", "Custom"}),
    #"Promoted Headers" = Table.PromoteHeaders(cleanTable, [PromoteAllScalars=true]),
    #"Changed Type" = Table.TransformColumnTypes(#"Promoted Headers",{{"Õppekava + tähis", type text}, {"Kvalifitseeruv kokku", Int64.Type}, {"Vastuvõetav", Int64.Type}, {"Kinnitanud õppima tuleku", type text}}),
    #"Extracted Last Characters" = Table.TransformColumns(#"Changed Type", {{"Õppekava + tähis", each Text.End(_, 4), type text}}),
    addKP = Table.AddColumn(#"Extracted Last Characters", "kp", each Date.AddDays( getDate,-1), type date)
in
    addKP;

shared fn_SAIS_DA = let

  addSAISkvalifitseeruv = Table.AddColumn(expand_fakt_DAvana, "SAIS.kvalifitseeruv", each let dakvalif = if [DA.Kvalifitseeruv] = null then 0 else [DA.Kvalifitseeruv], result = [Kvalifitseeruv]-dakvalif in result, Int64.Type),
  addSAISkinnitanud = Table.AddColumn(addSAISkvalifitseeruv, "SAIS.kinnitanud", each let dakinni = if [DA.Kinnitanud] = null then 0 else [DA.Kinnitanud], result = [Kinnitanud õppima tuleku]- dakinni in result, Int64.Type)

  addSAISkinnitanud;

shared vvCalendar_2024 = let
    Source = vvCalendar_alates2023,
    #"Filtered Rows" = Table.SelectRows(Source, each Date.Year([Date])=2024),
    #"Filtered Rows1" = Table.SelectRows(#"Filtered Rows", each [wk] >= 10 and [wk] <= 40),
    #"Filtered Rows2" = Table.SelectRows(#"Filtered Rows1", each ([weekNum] = 1)),
  #"Removed other columns" = Table.SelectColumns(#"Filtered Rows2", {"key", "wk"})

    #"Removed other columns";
shared vvCalendar_alates2023 = let
  date2024 = Table.FromList( List.Dates(#date(2024,3,4), 30, #duration(7,0,0,0)), Splitter.SplitByNothing(), type table [Date=Date.Type]),
  date2023 = Table.FromList( List.Dates(#date(2023,3,4), 30, #duration(7,0,0,0)), Splitter.SplitByNothing(), type table [Date=Date.Type]),
  date2025 = Table.FromList( List.Dates(#date(2025,3,4), 30, #duration(7,0,0,0)), Splitter.SplitByNothing(), type table [Date=Date.Type]),
  Custom = Table.Combine({date2025, date2024, date2023}),
  addWk = Table.AddColumn(Custom, "wk", each if Date.Year([Date])=2023 then Date.WeekOfYear([Date])+1 else Date.WeekOfYear([Date]), Int64.Type) ,
  addKey = Table.AddColumn(addWk, "key", each let mm = Text.BeforeDelimiter(Text.From([Date]), "/"), dd = Text.BetweenDelimiters(Text.From([Date]), "/", "/"), result = dd & ".0"&mm in result, type text),
  #"Added custom" = Table.AddColumn(addKey, "aasta", each Date.Year([Date]), Int64.Type)
in
  #"Added custom";
